            "Building sentiment features (LM 10-X) ...\n",
            "  ticker->CIK bridge: 108 of 110 tickers mapped\n",
            "  LM columns detected: {'CIK': 'CIK', 'FILING_DATE': 'FILING_DATE', 'N_Words': 'N_Words', 'Negative': 'N_Negative', 'Positive': 'N_Positive', 'Uncertainty': 'N_Uncertainty', 'Litigious': 'N_Litigious', 'N_Negation': 'N_Negation'}\n",
